quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  49,14,"Ŵarabu ŵanchimisi ŵatite: “Tukulupilile.” Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Nganinkulupilile. Nambo n’jileje: ‘Tulipeleeche (pakuŵa Asilamu).’ Ligongo mpaka sano chikulupi nganichijinjile m’mitima mwenu (ni kutamilichika). Sano naga nkunkunda Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, ngampunguchisya chilichose mu (malipilo ga) itendo yenu. Chisimu Allah ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope.”"
  49,15,"Chisimu ŵakulupilila ni aŵala ŵankulupilile Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ, kaneka ni nganakaichila, ni kuputa ngondo ni chipanje chao ni achimisyene ŵakwe petala lya Allah, ŵanganyao ni ŵali ŵakuona (pa chikulupi chao)"
  49,16,"Jilani: “Ana jenumanja nkummanyisya Allah dini jenu, kutendaga Allah jukumanyilila ya kumawunde ni petaka? Soni Allah chindu chilichose aŵele Jwaachimanya chenene.”"
  49,17,"Akunkuumba ligongo lyanti ajiinjiile mu Usilamu (mpela kuti antendele ukoto mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ). Jilani: “Nkaanguumba nako kwinjila kwenu mu Usilamu. Nambo Allah ni jwantendele ukoto jenumanja ligongo lyanti an’jongolele ku chikulupi, nam’baga jenumanja ŵakuona (pa chikulupi chenu).”"
  49,18,"Chisimu Allah akumanyilila yakusisika ya kumawunde ni petaka, soni Allah ni Nkuilolechesya yankutenda"
  50,1,Qâf. Ngujilumbila Qur’an jakuchimbichika (kuti tinchiukulidwa m’malembe)
  50,2,"Nambo akusimonga ya kwaichilila nkutetela (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwakuumila mu ŵanyapeo. Basi achimakafili ni akutiji: “Achi ni chindu chakusimosya.”"
  50,3,"“Ana patuchiwapo, ni kusyuka litaka (chisimu uwwe tuchiukulidwa)? Kwalakweko ni kuwuja kwakutalichila (kwangaŵa nkupatikana).”"
  50,4,"Chisimu Uwwe tukumanyilila yaikupungusya litaka mwajamanjao (mu ilu yao ndema jaakuola m’malembe), soni Kukwetu kwana Chitabu chakusunga (chilichose Al-Lauh Al-Mahfȗz)"
  50,5,"Nambo ayikaaniile yakuona ndema ja yaichilile, ni ali mu kaŵe kecholoŵane (akulepela kulekanganya sikati ja yakuona ni yaunami)"
  50,6,Ana ngaakuliona liwunde pachanya pao yatutite kalitaŵe kakwe ni kalisalalisye kakwe! Soni nganilikola mapesa
  50,7,"Ni litaka tulijasesye, ni tuŵisile palakwepo yakunyichisya (matumbi), ni tumesisye palakwepo ntundu uliose (wa mmela) wakusalala"
  50,8,(Kuti iŵe yalakweyi) yakuwugula meso ni yakunkumbusya kapolo jwalijose jwakuwujila (kwa Allah pakutenda toba)
  50,9,"Ni tutulwisye kuumila kwinani mesi gaupile (wula), ni tumesyisye ni galakwego migunda kwisa soni songolo syaagungulidwa"
  50,10,Ni mitende jelewulewu jajikwete itungatunga ya isogosi yakonyokonyo
  50,11,"(Kuŵa) lisiki lya achikapolo (Ŵetu), ni tukuchisyusyaga nago (mesigo) chilambo chachiwe, iyyoyopeyo ni mukuchiŵela kopoka (kwa m’malembe)"
  50,12,"Ŵaakaaniile paujo pao (Makuraishi nkanigaiche) ŵandu ŵa Nuhu, achimisyene chisima ni achina Samuda"
  50,13,"Ni achina Adi, Firiauna ni achalongo achimijakwe Lutwi"
  50,14,"Ni akutama nyyitekete (ŵandu ŵa Shuaibu), ni ŵandu ŵa Tubba‘i (ŵa ku Yemeni), ŵaliose mwa jamanjao ŵaakaaniile Achimitenga, basi ni chasimichiche chitetelo Changu (pa ŵanganyao)"
  50,15,"Ana ni twapesile ni gumba kwandanda? (Ngwamba), nambo ŵanganyao ali mu kaichila ya gumba kwasambano"
  50,16,"Soni chisimu Uwwe tun’gumbile mundu, ni tukumanyilila yaikunsongonela ntima wakwe, soni Uwwe tuli dusi nnope kwa jwalakwe (ni umanyilisi Wetu) kupunda ntasi ŵakuuta myasi (wannukosi mwakwe)"
  50,17,(Kumbuchilani) katema kaakupochela (itendo ya mundu ni kuilemba) akupochela ŵaŵili (Achimalaika) ŵaakutama chakun’dyo ni chakunchiji
  50,18,"Ngaakulumukulaga (mundu) liloŵe lililyose, ikaŵeje kukwakwe kukuŵa kwana nkwembecheya jwatayali (kulemba)"
  50,19,"Ni kuuchiyika kolelwa kwa chiwa mwakuonaonape, (ni tachisalilidwa mundu yanti): “Ayi ni ayila yamwaliji nkuiŵambala.”"
  50,20,"Ni lichigombedwa lipenga, lyele ni lisiku lyaipotesi"
  50,21,Ni tachiyika mundu jwalijose ni akunchiinga ni akuntendela umboni (ŵachilaika)
  50,22,"(Tachisalilidwa nkuleeŵa kuti): “Chisimu mmwe mwaliji nkukwanjila ya yalakweyi, basi tum’bunukwile chisiŵilo chenu, mwanti liso lyenu lelo lili lyakutema.”"
  50,23,"Ni tachiŵecheta n’jakwe jwangalekangana najo (lilaika lyalyalembaga masengo gakwe): “Ayi ni yaili kukwangu tayali (yamasengo gakwe gangalumbana).”"
  50,24,"(Allah tachalamula Achimalaika ŵaŵili ŵala lyakuchiinga ni lyakutendela umboni kuti): “Mumponyaani ku Jahannama jwalijose jwakufulu nnope, jwamakani.”"
  50,25,"“Jwakusiŵilila yambone, jwakusumba mpika, jwakaichila.”"
  50,26,"“Ajula juŵaŵisile nnungu jwine (jwakun’galagatila) pampepe ni Allah, basi mumponyani mu ilagasyo yawukali.”"